    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay running and requires significant mechanical diagnostics, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The exterior shows several large dents, significant paint fading, and areas of surface rust, and the interior has seen heavy wear with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest time and resources into major repairs to get this car back on the road safely.",
      "price": 4500.0,
